
IMAPStore kindrobot-remote
Host imap.migadu.com
Port 993
User stef@kindrobot.ca
PassCmd "pass show muw/stef@kindrobot.ca"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore kindrobot-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/kindrobot/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/kindrobot/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel kindrobot
Expunge Both
Far  :kindrobot-remote:
Near :kindrobot-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile

